metadata.bio:
HYBS (aka James Alyn Wee & Karn Kasidej) is a Bangkok-based duo, formed by two long lost friends who haven’t met each other for 8 years. They shared their love in laidback Pop/R&B tunes filled with special memories on their lives, layering with immaculate sound design in pursuit of their own HYBS’ vibes.

HYBS stands for Have You Been Shrimp.
